js&quot;]\" data-block-type=\"1337\" data-definition-name=\"website.components.html\" data-sqsp-block=\"text\" data-website-component-id=\"2ba61d53682c1efd9a67\" id=\"block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67\"><div class=\"sqs-block-content\"><div class=\"sqs-text-block-container\">\n  \n  <div class=\"sqs-html-content\" data-sqsp-text-block-content><h4 style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">現代キッチンに求められるのは、機能性だけではなく、暮らしの美学。</h4><p class=\"\" style=\"white-space:pre-wrap;\">台湾発のブランド「帝雉石」は、確かな製造技術と厳選された素材によって、デザイン性と実用性を兼ね備えた理想的なワークトップを提供しています。<br> 数多くのデザイナーやハイエンドユーザーから選ばれる理由は、その品質の安定性と細部へのこだわりにあります。</p></div>\n\n\n  \n<style id=\"container-styles\">#block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67 {\n    \n    --stroke-style: none;--stroke-thickness: 6px;\n    \n      \n      \n      \n    \n\n--tweak-text-block-background-color: initial;\n\n  }\n\n  #block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67 .sqs-html-content {\n    \n    --tweak-text-block-padding: 6% 6% 6% 6%;\n  --tweak-text-block-padding: initial;\n}\n\n  #block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67 {\n      mix-blend-mode: var(--tweak-text-block-blend\n  );\n      border-radius: var(--tweak-text-block-radius);\n  }\n\n  \n  \n#block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67 {\n      --tweak-text-block-radius: 0px 0px 0px 0px;\n    }\n\n\n  \n  \n\n  #block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67 {\n    }\n\n</style>\n\n<style id=\"override-container-styles\">\n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n            \n\n#block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67 {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  \n    @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          #block-2ba61d53682c1efd9a67 .sqs-html-content {\n            \n            }\n        }\n    \n  @media screen and (max-width: 767px) {\n          \n          \n\n          \n          \n          \n        }</style>\n\n<style class=\"transform-overrides-vars\">\n    \n  </style>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div><div class=\"sqs-block website-component-block sqs-block-website-component sqs-block-spacer spacer-block sized vsize-1\" data-block-css=\"[&quot;https://definitio